### ============================================
### 1. CREAR CLIENTES (POST)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Crear Cliente 1: Juan Perez (JSON)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "idClient": 1001,
  "idPerson": "12345678X",
  "email": "juan.perez@ejemplo.com",
  "phone": "600112233",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10",
  "namePerson": "Juan Perez",
  "registrationDate": "2026-02-02"
}

### 1.2 Crear Cliente 2: Ana Garcia (XML)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients
Content-Type: application/xml
Accept: application/xml

<client>
    <idClient>1002</idClient>
    <idPerson>98765432Y</idPerson>
    <email>ana.garcia@test.es</email>
    <phone>677889900</phone>
    <address>Avenida Diagonal 500</address>
    <namePerson>Ana Garcia</namePerson>
    <registrationDate>2025-12-31</registrationDate>
</client>

### ============================================
### 2. OBTENER CLIENTES (GET)
### ============================================

### 2.1 Obtener Cliente por ID 1001 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1001
Accept: application/json

### 2.2 Obtener Cliente por ID 1001 (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1001
Accept: application/xml

### 2.3 Obtener Cliente por ID 1002 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1002
Accept: application/json

### 2.4 Obtener Cliente por ID 1002 (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1002
Accept: application/xml

### ============================================
### 3. ACTUALIZAR CLIENTES (PUT)
### ============================================

### 3.1 Actualizar Cliente 1: Cambiar email y teléfono (JSON)
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1001
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "idClient": 1001,
  "idPerson": "12345678X",
  "email": "juan.perez.nuevo@email.com",
  "phone": "600999888",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10, Apto 5",
  "namePerson": "Juan Perez",
  "registrationDate": "2026-02-02"
}

### 3.2 Actualizar Cliente 2: Cambiar dirección y email (XML)
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1002
Content-Type: application/xml
Accept: application/xml

<client>
    <idClient>1002</idClient>
    <idPerson>98765432Y</idPerson>
    <email>ana.garcia.nueva@test.es</email>
    <phone>677111222</phone>
    <address>Calle Nueva 789, Barcelona</address>
    <namePerson>Ana Garcia</namePerson>
    <registrationDate>2025-12-31</registrationDate>
</client>

### 3.3 Verificar actualización del Cliente 1 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1001
Accept: application/json

### 3.4 Verificar actualización del Cliente 2 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1002
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### 4. ELIMINAR CLIENTE
### ============================================

### 4.1 Borrar Cliente 1
DELETE http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1001

### 4.2 Borrar Cliente 2
DELETE http://localhost:8080/softlearning/clients/1002